1. Why compression

主要应用在data transmission 和 data archiving。

1.1 data transmission

Wireless networks are the common infrastructure used for transmitting the data from the scanning system to remote workstations. 

数据量如果太大，在远程传送的过程中就存在诸多困难，所以为了实现快速高效传送，point cloud compression 就很有必要了。

1.2 data archiving

数据归档，指的是把暂时不用的老数据先存储起来，类似于档案馆的作用。 所以point cloud compression 也就很重要了。

2. compression methods 

2.1 based on tree structures

k-d tree
octree

2.2 binary formats

当初评估KITTI data set时候，它们存储的Lidar数据就是二进制的格式。

2.2.1 LAS

The American Society of Photogrammetry and Remote Sensing (ASPRS) created a simple
binary exchange format called the LAS format.

2.2.2 LAZ

LAZ is a lossless compressor for LiDAR data stored in the LAS format.
 
